06:51.562 --> 06:54.508
They all know the other fella packs a gun.

06:55.049 --> 06:57.535
Everybody does his best to act just right.

06:57.715 --> 07:00.962
Cause there's gonna be a funeral if they start a fight.

07:01.202 --> 07:04.008
They struggle and they shuffle till we're all daylight.

07:04.028 --> 07:06.634
Yes, they all go native on a Saturday.

07:06.634 --> 07:26.172 
